          <div class="mush-benefits">
            <div class="mush-benefit"><span class="mush-benefit-icon">🔬</span><div><strong>Nerve Growth Factor (NGF)</strong><p>Lion's Mane stimulates the production of NGF — a protein critical for the growth, maintenance, and survival of nerve cells. More NGF means better neural connectivity.</p></div></div>
